nodes.text: Lenk was a Twi'lek female who was a member of the Free Ryloth Movement early in the Imperial Era. She participated in a mission to rescue several rebels arrested by the Galactic Empire after being caught smuggling weapons. However, most of the freedom fighters, including Lenk, were captured in an Imperial ambush. However, she and the other freedom fighters were rescued from Imperial custody by Clone Force 99.
Lenk was voiced by Shelby Young in Star Wars: The Bad Batch.
